title: 650. Reaction to Carson Wentz's Trade to Colts + Daniel Jeremiah's Mock Draft 2.0
itunes:title: 650. Reaction to Carson Wentz's Trade to Colts + Daniel Jeremiah's Mock Draft 2.0
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the Philadelphia Eagles trading quarterback Carson Wentz to the Indianapolis Colts and further look at both sides of the trade (:22). Next, Daniel Jeremiah gives a breakdown of his full first round 2021 NFL mock draft 2.0 (27:41). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
